Dp-c%E1%BA%A3nh-h%E1%BB%B7-v%C5%A9/poem-DngBU4bE6YtLWXhvchnCjA">Nhập cảnh hỷ vũ - 入境喜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-l-vfhV6KqRexQyEkpib8Ng">Đặng Huy Trứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/S%C3%A0i-m%C3%B4n/poem-vg2174OhgSqPjoq6H1VPpg">Sài môn - 柴門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ho%C3%A0ng-t%C3%A2y-tu%E1%BA%A7n-nam-kinh-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-06/poem-BL8Vuq0lq1iX2yAw2y1goA">Thượng hoàng tây tuần nam kinh ca kỳ 06 - 上皇西巡南京歌其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%C3%A1n/V%C4%83n/poem-ubDVVIoD3ejWyyJRCM9pkQ">Văn - 蚊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%C3%A1n/author-Nx2AggB5pgAGcLiAEumXWg">Vũ Cán</a>)<br></div>	</div>
